<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.203373>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 8. Eukoenenia ferratilis sp. n. 1, frontal organ of female 3, dorsal view; 2, lateral organ of female 3, dorsal view (scale bar 20 µm); 3, propeltidial chaetotaxy of female 2 (scale bar 100 µm); 4, metapeltidial setae of female 2 (scale bar 50 µm); 5, deuto-tritosternal setae of female 3 (scale bar 40 µm); 6, chelicera of female 3 (scale bar 100 µm); 7, basitarsus 3 – 4 of leg I of female 4 (scale bar 40 µm); 8, basitarsus IV of female 4 (scale bar 40 µm)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/203373/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.203374>
    dc:description "FIGURES 9 – 14. Eukoenenia ferratilis sp. n. 9, coxa I of female 3; 10, coxa II of female 3; 11, coxa III of female 3; 12, coxa IV of female 3 (scale bar 60 µm); 13, opisthosoma of female 1, dorsal view; 14, opisthosoma of female 1, ventral view (scale bar 300 µm)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/203374/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.203375>
    dc:description "FIGURES 15 – 17. Eukoenenia ferratilis sp. n. 15, genitalia of female 3 (scale bar 60 µm); 16, genitalia of male (scale bar 60 µm); 17, bta IV of immature stage A (scale bar 40 µm)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/203375/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

